      <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/amen-bank-mobile-app/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start gap-8&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;shrink-0&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;images/amen-logo.png&#34; alt=&#34;Amen Bank&#34; class=&#34;w-32 h-32 object-contain bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-md border border-border-primary dark:border-border-primary p-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;text-lg text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary leading-relaxed&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;mb-4&#34;&gt;&lt;strong class=&#34;text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary font-bold&#34;&gt;Redefining Mobile Banking:&lt;/strong&gt; The Amen Bank mobile application is a major banking application built with robust clean architecture principles. It delivers a secure, highly performant, and seamless banking experience to users, enabling them to manage their finances effortlessly on the go without compromising on enterprise-grade security.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-12 text-center&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.amenmobile.amenbank&amp;hl=en&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34; class=&#34;block p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-secondary dark:bg-bg-secondary border border-border-primary dark:border-border-primary shadow-sm hover:border-primary transition-colors&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;text-3xl font-bold text-primary dark:text-primary-light mb-2&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fab fa-google-play&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;text-sm text-text-tertiary dark:text-text-tertiary uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold&#34;&gt;Google Play Store&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://apps.apple.com/tn/app/amen-mobile/id1144455485&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34; class=&#34;block p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-secondary dark:bg-bg-secondary border border-border-primary dark:border-border-primary shadow-sm hover:border-primary transition-colors&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;text-3xl font-bold text-primary dark:text-primary-light mb-2&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fab fa-apple&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;text-sm text-text-tertiary dark:text-text-tertiary uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold&#34;&gt;Apple App Store&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;space-y-12&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;section&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-text-primary mb-6 flex items-center gap-3&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;span class=&#34;w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-primary flex items-center justify-center text-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-wallet&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;Comprehensive Digital Banking&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;bg-bg-secondary dark:bg-bg-secondary border border-border-primary dark:border-border-primary rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p class=&#34;text-text-secondary dark:text-text-secondary mb-6 leading-relaxed&#34;&gt;The Amen Mobile application translates the complete physical branch experience into a secure, intuitive digital platform, offering users end-to-end control over their financial operations directly from their pocket.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
